    - "Test vectors verified with lodash.takeright@4.0.1 via Node.js 22.22.1 on Ubuntu 26.04 / Docker, 2026-04-24"
  not_derived_from:
    - "lodash source"
  notes:
    - "lodash.takeright exports the _.takeRight function directly as module.exports."
    - "takeRight(array, n) returns a slice of n elements taken from the end."
    - "Defaults to n=1 if omitted."
